TITLE: Pervyj pryzhok
AUTHOR: Igor Getzls
DATE OF CREATION: 17.02.2026
FIRST PUBLICATION:
- stihi.ru (author cabinet), 17.02.2026 13:38  MSK 
Publication Certificate No. 126021704915   
